OL,6,GThe BBC decision to remove Gary Lineker
OL,7,Gfrom his presenting role in a row over
OL,8,Gimpartiality has impacted some of BBC
OL,9,GSport's biggest programme brands this
OL,10,Gweekend.
OL,12,FOn Friday evening, the BBC announced it
OL,13,Fhad told Gary Lineker to step back from
OL,14,Fpresenting Match of the Day until
OL,15,Fagreement is reached on his use of
OL,16,Fsocial media. The corporation said it
OL,17,Fregarded Lineker's "recent social media
OL,18,Factivity to be a breach of our
OL,19,Fguidelines".
